title: BTEAM Town Hall with Bobby and Listeners: The Truth Behind Lunchbox Guessing Weights + Will Bobby Write Another Book?
itunes:title: BTEAM Town Hall with Bobby and Listeners: The Truth Behind Lunchbox Guessing Weights + Will Bobby Write Another Book?
description:
Bobby invited 5 listeners from the BTEAM Facebook page to ask him each a couple questions about the show, him and more. The topics range from what TV couple he thinks resembles his relationship, if he will write another book in the future and what happened to the segment where Lunchbox guesses callers weights.
